{
  "stem": "19211.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 381.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because when you pass away, something, people take it too hard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want them to get too attached.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but that's--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my folks passed away and we so much-- when they died--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went together, so much through, together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were so devoted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're ready to give their lives away for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's more than an average.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Parents die.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we expect that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was more than that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sorry to say that we were so close all together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They gave their lives away for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would have given their life away for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, time heals a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't dwell on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know that we all have to die sometimes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I do not dwell on it, because we had happy years together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what I think about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But still, it's-- when you're closer together, closer to death, it's harder to take.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What were your occupations since you came to United States?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I started here like I told you, the labor gang there in the rubber factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I went-- well, I became a machine operator, machinist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that, I-- before I went to college here, I remember I went to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncle lived in Detroit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stayed with him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got a little job in a private-- because I was an engineer, I got a draftsman-- became a draftsman for him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't doing so well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I didn't have enough training in that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the job didn't work out too well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lucky for me, I came back to Canton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't want to look for another job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's when I went and enrolled in Akron U.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
